<item>
            <title>[LUDOC-557] Document qos_maxage</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-557</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Add documentation for the qos_maxage parameter which controls how long&lt;br/&gt;
cached filesystem statistics remain valid before being refreshed from&lt;br/&gt;
OSTs/MDTs during QoS stripe allocation. Currently undocumented despite&lt;br/&gt;
being an important tuning parameter for balancing allocation accuracy&lt;br/&gt;
vs system overhead.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Adds detailed section in ManagingStripingFreeSpace.xml and reference&lt;br/&gt;
entry in LustreProc.xml.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
